=====================================================
PLAYING INFO:
The song is best played fingerpicking arpeggios for
most of the song, to emulate the sweeping harp.
For the Am7 to D9 pizzicato sections and also the
bar of D9 at the end of the verses, pluck the strings
together simultaneously on each beat.
    Am7         D9
e|-----------|-----------|-----------|
B|--1--1--1--|--1--1--1--|--1--1--1--|
G|--0--0--0--|--2--2--2--|--2--2--2--|
D|-----------|--0--2--4--|--2--0-----|
A|--0--2--3--|-----------|--------3--|
E|-----------|-----------|-----------|

